dct_description_sm: Base map of Hobart and suburbs showing statistical and municipal boundaries. "NMO/54/129." "Local government areas (City and Municipality) as used in Commonwealth Census 30th June, 1954." This is the base map of the "Metropolitan map" referred to on state map : Statistical divisions of Tasmania : [1954 census].
dct_creator_sm: Australia. Commonwealth Bureau of Census and Statistics
